#Summary1=(human1) On May 30, Marcie Rickenbacker writes a letter to her Mum from Abbot Academy about school acceptances, exams, a love interest named Brendan and his academic endeavors, and other small monetary matters, and also writes about trouble she has shipping things home.

#Summary2=(claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022) In a letter to her mother, Marcie discusses school concerns like exams and coed options, mentions sending a package home, shares news about Brendan going to Antioch, requests five dollars for her return trip home, and sends greetings to family.

#Summary3=(gpt4o) On May 30, Marcie writes to her mom thanking her for her note, expressing concerns about choosing a coed school, detailing her mailing logistics and upcoming exams, sharing news about her boyfriend potentially starting at Antioch, requesting five dollars for expenses, asking about a check, and hoping for good weather to study outside, while sending regards to everyone.

#Summary4=(Meta-Llama-3-8B-Instruct) Marcie writes to her mother about receiving her note, plans for exams and a potential summer setback with her boyfriend Brendan, and asks for money to cover expenses on her way home.

#Summary5=(Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct) Marcie writes to her mother about receiving a letter, her concerns about attending a northern coeducational school, sending items via postal mail due to issues with UPS, upcoming exams, the impending departure of her boyfriend Brendan, and her request for money to cover expenses and send a gift.
#Text=Miss Marcie Rickenbacker
#Text=Abbot Academy
#Text=Andover , Massachusetts 01810
#Text=May 30
#Text=Mum ,
#Text=Got your note today , many thanks , it was good to hear from you .
#Text=What did you do with duck ?
#Text=What am I going to do about that coed school in the north ?
#Text=There are n’t very many good ones around , ( that I could get into ) .
#Text=We ca n’t send stuff UPS because it ’s out of Boston and for some reason it ’s too much trouble .
#Text=So ^ Today I sent a box of stuff home regular ( parcel post ) mail .
#Text=Mrs. B put the postage on ( 80 ¢ ) but I just know it ’s not going to be enough .
#Text=My exams start on Monday , Eng , French , then Math ( M. - Wed )
#Text=No his. of Art. exam !
#Text=Yeah ! ! !
#Text=Icky news for me – Brendan ( my love of this month ) is going to Antioch and they start June 30 .
#Text=He ’s trying to go the next session ; Sept 29th , but wo n’t hear for another week or two .
#Text=I ’m going to keep my fingers crossed , I was really planning on seeing him this summer .
#Text=I hate to ask this , but … could you send me a measly five bucks ( only 5 smackers ) so I can get home .
#Text=At this point I have just barely enough to get home , but I want to get something for Mlle. Arosa and then as always there ’ll be other petty expenses .
#Text=Please … .
#Text=Also tell Nance to cash the check if she has n’t already , it ’s fouling me up .
#Text=I hope it stays nice , so I can study all morning outside .
#Text=Today it was in the 80's .
#Text=Say “ hello ” to all for me .
#Text=Love always ,
#Text=Marcie
#Text=See you soon !
